reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cheaply made but it works?
reviews.reviewText: This was fairly easy to assemble, but instructions literally look like someone had a printed it out on regular printer paper and cut it in half.There was no indication what the white hook things were (which I assume is to hang things.. but I wouldn't recommend it as it easily tips).The material itself feels cheap, to be fair.. it did look cheap in the picture as well.Now it does work for what I ordered it for- a place to organize my crafting supply. I don't think it would look good as what they're advertising it for .. like as a bathroom caddy... I personally would spend a bit extra to get a nicer looking one for my bathroom

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Pretty easy enough to assemble, could mesh a little better. Didn’t have instructions for the white pieces so I assume it’s for hanging things based on the product photos. Definitely works for managing minimal storage space so a good value for the price.
